[section#library.c
    [:en] The C standard library
    [:zh_CN] C 标准程序库
]

[para]
[:en]
The [=Cpp] standard library also makes available the facilities of the C
standard library, [% library[!C standard]] suitably adjusted to ensure static
type safety.
[:zh_CN]
[=Cpp] 标准程序库中还可使用 [%程序库 [!C 标准～]] C 标准程序库中的功能，它们已经
经过调整以确保静态类型安全性。

[para]
[:en]
The descriptions of many library functions rely on the C standard library for
the semantics of those functions.
[:zh_CN]
许多库函数的描述依赖于 C 标准程序库中这些函数的语义。

[:en]
In some cases, the signatures specified in this document may be different from
the signatures in the C standard library, and additional overloads may be
declared in this document, but the behavior and the preconditions (including any
preconditions implied by the use of an ISO C [`restrict] qualifier) are the same
unless otherwise stated.
[:zh_CN]
某些情况下，本文档所给出的签名与在 C 标准程序库中的签名有所不同，并且本文档会
提供额外的重载，但其行为和前条件（包括由使用 ISO C 的 [`restrict] 限定符所蕴含的
前条件），除非另行指明，否则都是相同的。
